item.title: CVE-2023-5763|2024-08-02T08:07:32.848Z -- eclipse%20foundation -- glassfish
item.description: In Eclipse Glassfish 5 or 6, running with old versions of JDK (lower than 6u211, or < 7u201, or < 8u191), allows remote attackers to load malicious code on the server via access to insecure ORB listeners.
